          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/heoimocc/">热雨</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3931920981">2023-09-15 19:04:28</a>
          <span class="comment-location">山东</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">我是堕落的天使，我要把寒山当作英雄，我要享受沿着鹿径下山的孤独时光，我要寻找一条纯粹的道路，寻找被我称作诗的东西，我要做自由的人，不管世界怎样。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/3151990/?comment_id=3931920981"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

      </ul>
